@inherits LayoutComponentBase

@* The app shell (40.2): persistent primary nav + a content region hosting the active surface.
   `.app-frame` is column-reverse on mobile (content above, bottom tab bar below) and a row on
   desktop (left rail, content right). /login opts out via BareLayout, so this only ever frames an
   authenticated surface. *@
<div class="app-frame">
    <NavShell />
    <main id="main" class="app-content">@Body</main>
</div>
